@startuml FR-08_Basic_Inventory_Alerts

title Activity Diagram: FR-08 - Low Inventory Flag

|Lab Asset Manager|
start

:Select Item to Mark as Consumable;

:Set Minimum Quantity Threshold;

|System|
:Save Item as Consumable with Threshold;

:Consumable Item Configuration Complete;

stop

|System|
start

:Item Quantity Updated;
note right
  Triggered when consumable
  item quantity changes
end note

if (Quantity < Minimum Threshold?) then (yes)
  :Flag Item as "Low Stock";
  
  :Update Item Status;
  
else (no)
  :Keep Current Status;
endif

stop

|Lab Asset Manager|
start

:View Consumable Items List;

|System|
:Retrieve All Consumable Items;

:Display Items with Stock Status;
note right
  Shows:
  - Item Name
  - Current Quantity
  - Minimum Threshold
  - Status (Low Stock flag if applicable)
end note

|Lab Asset Manager|
:Review Low Stock Items;

stop

@enduml